reviewText: This recording is among the few videos available to the public with such intimate and extensive exposure to Antonio Carlos (Tom)Jobim, Vinicius de Moraes and Toquinho,artists who are icons of Bossa  Nova and Brazilian music. Recorded in an intimate setting in a night club in Italy for a TV show, it is a must for the Brazilian music afficianado.
